Unocal replaces 101 pct of 1996 oil & gas . Unocal Corp said it replaced 101 percent of its net worldwide oil and gas production in 1996 as it continued its aggressive development of energy resources overseas . The company ' s worldwide replacement rate excludes the impact of reserve sales , including most of Unocal ' s California oil and gas properties , during the year . It said it replaced 234 percent of its foreign production on a barrel - of - oil - equivalent ( BOE ) basis with major oil and gas additions from new and existing fields in Thailand , Myanmar Indonesia , and Azerbaijan . 
